Hm, is there a reason why you&#x27;ve not declared something like &quot;const VGABUF: int = 0xb8000;&quot; (like I assume VGA_WIDTH is defined?)?<p><pre><code>    pub unsafe fn putchar(x: u16, y: u16, c: u8) {
        let idx : uint =  (y * VGA_WIDTH * 2 + x * 2) as uint;
        // 0xb8000 is the VGA buffer
        *((0xb8000 + idx) as *mut u16) = make_vgaentry(c, Black, Yellow);
}</code></pre>
